1️⃣ TIME & WORK – ADVANCED (EFFICIENCY)

Today we learn efficiency, which makes Time & Work questions much easier.

🔹 A. WHAT IS EFFICIENCY?

Efficiency = work done in one unit time

If A finishes work in 5 days

👉 Efficiency of A = 1/5

If B finishes work in 10 days

👉 Efficiency of B = 1/10

Higher efficiency → less time needed

